A market exchange where bitcoins can be bought and sold.  Funds may be deposited by mailing in cash.  Funds may be withdrawn as cash mailed to you.

Bitcoin2cash, LLC is an entity registered in the State of Alabama (1.1).

The site matches bids and asks periodically (every 5 minutes).

##History

The site was originally announced on July 13th, 2010 (2.1). The site was subsequently redesigned and the new availability was announced on April 2nd, 2011 (2.2).

